<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ʋba Pi̱ki pulla hocha ƲIT15</title>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki pulla hocha
 Nana achukma ka
 Pim apihi̱sa pulla na,
 Yakoht e ma̱yʋshke.

[V2]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki ak keyukma,
 Pishno ak inli kʋt
 Nan isht ilaiyukpa yoka
 Il ithaiyana wa.

[V3]
 Hʋpi chu̱kʋsh pulla hoka
 Mominchi fehna hosh
 Pi̱ki ʋba pulla hoka
 Il ema pullashke.

[V4]
 Anumpa ilbʋsha fehnʋt
 Ʋba Pi̱ki yoka
 Il im asilhha pulla cha,
 Il im antiashke.

[V5]
 Si okcha̱ya ta̱kla hocha
 Ʋm ʋlhtaha tukmʋt;
 Chisʋs a binili hoka
 Pisa li pullashke.

[V6]
 Heh ahni bieka hocha
 Pi chu̱kʋsh atukma
 Anukfihinli fehna hosh,
 Iloh aiashashke.

[V7]
 Hʋpi yʋmohmi hatukmʋt
 Ʋba Pi̱ki ʋno
 Eho pihi̱sa hinla kʋt
 E holitoblashke.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>15</hymn_number>
</song>